Detailed Description

template<class CONTAINER>
class STLUtility::co_dumper< CONTAINER >

Container dumper.

<br /> Class for dumping stuff to mc2dbg8 etc. Needed since they are defined as if ( false ) Use like so: vector<uint32> cont; mc2dbg << co_dump( cont, ",") << endl;
